Privacy Policy
This page is used to inform our users regarding our policies with the collection, use, and

disclosure of Personal Information if anyone decided to use our App.
Information Collection and Use
We don't collect any type of data and personal information regarding using the app without your permission.
App permissions and their use.
1-Permisson Camera:
We ask for this permission so that you can use your camera for realtime text Recognition (OCR).
2-Permisson Record Audio:
We ask for this permission so that you can record your voice and compatre it with TTS engine.
NOTE:
We do not upload , publish any of your data.